item.title: Apache Ant
item.dc:creator: @cr0ss cr0ss
item.description:
@cr0ss wrote:

Hi bonzakid, still having a problem?
Adding a PATH variable to Environment Variables WILL solve the problem, as it solved the problem for me, long time ago.
Right click on My Computer, select Properties, then go to Advanced tab and click on Environment Variables. Now under UPPER box (^) click NEW. Name is “PATH” (without "-s) and path is the location of your apache and bin folder. So it should be something like “C:/ApacheAnt/bin”(without the "-s). If you want to add more variables there, like JAVAC location etc, then just put “;” and add another path there.
It’s just that simple. : )
